# 2. Set your JWT_TOKEN (this is required)
# 3. Adjust API_BASE_URL if using a different RapidStor instance
# 4. Set DEBUG_MODE=true during development for better error messages
# 5. Adjust memory and timeout settings based on your server capabilities
# 6. Choose your preferred DEFAULT_LOCATION

# Note: Never commit your .env file to version control
# Add .env to your .gitignore file to keep your credentials safe